title: Group Anagrams
description: Given an array of strings, group the anagrams together. You can return the answer in any order. For the output, print each group of anagrams sorted alphabetically on a new line, and the lines themselves should be sorted alphabetically based on the first word of each group.
output_format: Each group of anagrams on a new line, sorted.
